net.proteusframework.core.prefs

Class DelegatingPreferences

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.prefs.Preferences
      • net.proteusframework.core.prefs.DelegatingPreferences

  • public abstract class DelegatingPreferences
extends java.util.prefs.Preferences
    A Preferences implementation that delegates to another implementation. Please note that use of this implementation implies that one cannot assume the underlying implementation and should not pass this object to preference factory methods that may require a specific preference implementation.
    Author:
    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com)

      • createUnderlying

        protected abstract java.util.prefs.Preferences createUnderlying()
        Create the underlying preference object, which is not to say an existing node cannot be returned. The point is that this method is called once per instantiation of the delegate and cached thereafter.
        Returns:
        Preferences.
